\par Robust and usable conservation science under climate change is needed at scales ranging from local to global. For example, preserve managers seek guidance about how to best steward natural resources for climate resilience \citep{Nadeau2015}, and  international climate policymakers rely on scientific data and publications for systematic observation of climate systems and impacts to people \cite{ipcc2007}. 

